quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  16,51,"Allah ka farmaan hai ke “do khuda na bana lo, khuda to bas ek hi hai, lihaza tum mujhi se daro"
  16,52,"Usi ka hai woh sab kuch jo aasmano mein hai aur jo zameen mein hai, aur khaalisan usi ka deen (saari qayinaat mein) chal raha hai. Phir kya Allah ko chodh kar tum kisi aur se taqwa (darr) karoge"
  16,53,Tumko jo niyamat bhi haasil hai Allah hi ki taraf se hai phir jab koi sakht waqt tumpar aata hai to tum log khud apni fariyadein lekar usi ki taraf daudte ho
  16,54,Magar jab Allah us waqt ko taal deta hai to yakayak tum mein se ek giroh apne Rubb ke saath dusron ko (is meharbani ke shukriye mein) shareek karne lagta hai
  16,55,"Taa-ke Allah ke ehsan ki nashukri karey, Accha mazey karlo, anqareeb tumhein maloom ho jayega"
  16,56,"Yeh log jinki haqeeqat se waqif nahin hain unke hissey hamare diye huye rizq mein se muqarrar karte hain. Khuda ki kasam, zaroor tumse pucha jayega ke yeh jhoot tumne kaise ghadh liye thay"
  16,57,"Yeh khuda ke liye betiyan tajweez karte hain, SubhanAllah! Aur inke liye woh jo yeh khud chahein"
  16,58,Jab in mein se kisi ko beti ke paida honay ki khush-khabri di jati hai to uske chehre par kaloons (grows dark) chaa jati hai aur woh bas khoon ka sa ghoont pee kar reh jata hai
  16,59,Logon se chupta phirta hai ke is buri khabar ke baad kya kisi ko mooh dikhaye. Sochta hai ke zillat ke saath beti ko liye rahey ya mitti mein daba de? Dekho kaise bure hukum hain jo yeh khuda ke barey mein lagate hain
  16,60,"Buri siffat se muttasaf (be ascribed) kiya janey ke layak to woh log hain jo aakhirat ka yaqeen nahin rakhte. Raha Allah, to uske liye sab se bartar siffat hain, wahi to sab par gaalib aur hikmat mein kamil hai"